Description: Use absolute paths for (Try)Exec in mpv.desktop
Origin: vendor
Debian-Bug: http://bugs.debian.org/728149
Forwarded: not-needed
Author: Alessandro Ghedini <ghedo@debian.org>
Last-Update: 2013-10-30

--- a/etc/mpv.desktop
+++ b/etc/mpv.desktop
@@ -18,8 +18,8 @@
 Comment[ru]=Воспроизвести фильмы и музыку
 Comment[zh]=多媒体播放器
 Icon=mpv
-TryExec=mpv
-Exec=mpv --no-terminal --force-window -- %U
+TryExec=/usr/bin/mpv
+Exec=/usr/bin/mpv --no-terminal --force-window -- %U
